        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">What is the difference between the 5 levels? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>GOLD: essential cleanse (€50). PLATINUM: cleanse + deep hydration with hyaluronic acid and vitamin C (€75). DETOX: cleanse + nano-needle peel + detox mask (€150). DIAMOND: cleanse + advanced equipment + 3 exfoliants (€150). ELITE: most complete protocol with plaster therapy and premium equipment (€200).</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">How often should you have a professional facial? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>It depends on your skin type: normal skin every 4-6 weeks; oily/acne-prone every 3-4 weeks; dry/mature every 6-8 weeks. We confirm cadence at your assessment.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">Are facials just wellness or do they have a real effect? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>They have a real clinical effect: manual comedone extraction, removal of dead cells, cell renewal stimulated by clinical equipment, deep hydration. They genuinely change the state of the skin, not just feel pleasant.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">Can I wear make-up or go out in the sun afterwards? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>We recommend no make-up for the first 4-6 hours so the skin can breathe. Always use sunscreen, especially during the first 24-48 hours.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-page-faq-item">
        <button class="cat-page-faq-q" type="button">Can you treat active acne or sensitive skin? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="cat-page-faq-a"><p>Yes, with an adapted protocol. For active acne we use a specific Anti-Acne Treatment beforehand. For sensitive skin we adjust products and intensity.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

